WEBVTT

00:01:06.336 --> 00:01:10.778
=The Truth=

00:01:11.480 --> 00:01:14.136
=Episode 2=

00:01:18.552 --> 00:01:19.472
You're all here.

00:01:20.832 --> 00:01:21.432
Zhao.

00:01:22.712 --> 00:01:24.033
You all look so beautiful today.

00:01:24.033 --> 00:01:24.753
You too.

00:01:24.753 --> 00:01:25.432
Exactly.

00:01:25.432 --> 00:01:26.593
You flatter me.

00:01:26.593 --> 00:01:27.712
Not at all.

00:01:27.912 --> 00:01:29.673
You look incredibly cool in this outfit.

00:01:29.673 --> 00:01:30.912
- That chain suits you.
- Little Zhao.

00:01:30.912 --> 00:01:31.960
(Han Zhao, Ye Qian's childhood friend)
Look, Ye Qian's here.

00:01:33.393 --> 00:01:34.313
Little Qian.

00:01:34.313 --> 00:01:35.313
Don't call me that.

00:01:36.113 --> 00:01:37.912
I've called you that since childhood.

00:01:37.912 --> 00:01:38.873
What should I call you?

00:01:39.472 --> 00:01:40.313
Baby Qian?

00:01:42.584 --> 00:01:43.432
Nice bike.

00:01:43.432 --> 00:01:44.920
Didn't you say you weren't coming?

00:01:45.393 --> 00:01:46.233
I changed my mind.

00:01:47.873 --> 00:01:48.873
Not coming, huh?

00:01:50.593 --> 00:01:51.472
No one's coming?

00:01:51.673 --> 00:01:52.472
Alright.

00:01:52.472 --> 00:01:53.352
No one's coming?

00:01:53.472 --> 00:01:54.953
You're having a blast, Liu.

00:01:55.873 --> 00:01:56.632
Qing.

00:01:57.313 --> 00:01:58.552
Got held up by something.

00:01:58.552 --> 00:01:59.513
Sorry, I'm late.

00:01:59.513 --> 00:02:01.192
Liu, have a seat.

00:02:01.432 --> 00:02:02.233
Let's continue.

00:02:03.832 --> 00:02:04.912
Really sorry about that.

00:02:43.793 --> 00:02:45.393
Is your racing legal here?

00:02:45.393 --> 00:02:47.393
All paperwork's in order.
Completely legal.

00:02:47.832 --> 00:02:49.633
The police deal with illegality.

00:03:07.073 --> 00:03:09.152
Well, after these three laps,

00:03:09.152 --> 00:03:10.992
Little Qian will be at least fourth.

00:03:12.513 --> 00:03:13.312
Don't believe me?

00:03:16.592 --> 00:03:17.393
Let's bet.

00:03:18.473 --> 00:03:20.992
Officers don't gamble.

00:03:22.673 --> 00:03:23.513
How boring.

00:03:23.712 --> 00:03:25.793
Just verbally, I know you're broke.

00:03:28.592 --> 00:03:29.393
Okay, let's bet.

00:03:29.673 --> 00:03:30.992
Qing, Liu.

00:03:31.832 --> 00:03:32.752
This one's on me.

00:03:50.592 --> 00:03:53.032
We'll fully compensate
for all damages here.

00:03:55.113 --> 00:03:56.992
I also apologize to you all
on Liu's behalf.

00:04:00.752 --> 00:04:01.793
However,

00:04:03.913 --> 00:04:05.113
keeping us waiting this long?

00:04:06.393 --> 00:04:07.913
Even for a first-time cooperation

00:04:08.393 --> 00:04:09.513
with mutual distrust,

00:04:10.113 --> 00:04:12.832
it's still too disrespectful.

00:04:15.312 --> 00:04:16.233
In business,

00:04:16.992 --> 00:04:18.113
rules matter most.

00:04:19.233 --> 00:04:22.033
Better to lose the deal than lose trust.

00:04:25.432 --> 00:04:26.432
Perhaps this trip

00:04:27.432 --> 00:04:28.593
was a mistake for us.

00:04:29.512 --> 00:04:30.312
Let's go, Liu.

00:04:31.233 --> 00:04:32.392
Qing, wait.

00:04:33.512 --> 00:04:37.312
We're very sincere
about this cooperation.

00:04:41.312 --> 00:04:42.113
Excuse me.

00:04:42.312 --> 00:04:43.113
Need to take this.

00:05:03.552 --> 00:05:04.713
Overtaking on a bend?

00:05:05.512 --> 00:05:06.392
It's too dangerous.

00:05:07.512 --> 00:05:09.473
You don't know Little Qian at all.

00:05:26.872 --> 00:05:27.673
Cool!

00:05:27.673 --> 00:05:28.552
Awesome!

00:05:31.392 --> 00:05:33.312
You two grew up together.

00:05:33.593 --> 00:05:34.913
You must know him well.

00:05:34.913 --> 00:05:35.992
Since you know him so well,

00:05:35.992 --> 00:05:37.833
why haven't you won him over yet?

00:05:40.593 --> 00:05:41.632
He told you that?

00:05:42.233 --> 00:05:43.593
Isn't it obvious?

00:05:44.913 --> 00:05:46.593
Ever since he moved into our dorm,

00:05:46.593 --> 00:05:47.793
you've visited so many times.

00:05:47.952 --> 00:05:49.793
Even the security guard
at the gate knows you.

00:05:50.233 --> 00:05:54.752
And that ring you always wear.

00:05:55.233 --> 00:05:56.432
It's made of plastic

00:05:56.713 --> 00:05:57.992
with badly worn paint.

00:05:57.992 --> 00:05:58.793
I think

00:05:58.793 --> 00:06:01.552
he gave it to you
when you played house as kids.

00:06:03.713 --> 00:06:04.552
Am I right?

00:06:14.512 --> 00:06:16.752
You flaunt it in front of him daily,

00:06:17.233 --> 00:06:18.992
yet he shows zero reaction.

00:06:20.312 --> 00:06:21.153
Two possibilities.

00:06:21.153 --> 00:06:21.872
First,

00:06:21.992 --> 00:06:24.673
he's completely rejected you
in his heart.

00:06:25.072 --> 00:06:25.713
Second,

00:06:26.233 --> 00:06:28.233
he forgot about this ages ago.

00:06:31.416 --> 00:06:33.464
Little Qian has always had someone
in his heart.

00:06:34.392 --> 00:06:35.192
And it's not me.

00:06:37.192 --> 00:06:39.872
I hear it's trendy now
for girls to pursue guys.

00:06:40.273 --> 00:06:41.552
Why not try pursuing me instead?

00:06:41.793 --> 00:06:42.713
For a change.

00:06:47.552 --> 00:06:48.192
Get lost.

00:06:54.392 --> 00:06:54.992
Okay.

00:06:57.632 --> 00:06:58.312
Qing,

00:06:59.312 --> 00:07:02.392
our boss, Xiang, wants a word with you.

00:07:21.673 --> 00:07:23.392
When can we meet Mr. Bao?

00:07:27.432 --> 00:07:29.392
What do you mean by 'the right time'?

00:07:31.033 --> 00:07:32.512
Can you speak for Huo?

00:07:36.392 --> 00:07:39.512
My words are Huo's words.

00:07:48.632 --> 00:07:50.072
Qiang's side is all set.

00:07:50.673 --> 00:07:52.273
I thought it would take more convincing.

00:07:52.632 --> 00:07:54.793
Didn't expect that woman
to agree so readily.

00:07:56.392 --> 00:07:59.593
This time, Huo sent his woman
to liaise with us.

00:08:00.473 --> 00:08:04.113
Seems he's taking this cooperation
pretty seriously.

00:08:05.913 --> 00:08:07.312
What's the name of Huo's woman?

00:08:07.952 --> 00:08:10.192
She is... Dan Qing.

00:08:10.713 --> 00:08:11.512
Dan Qing?

00:08:15.992 --> 00:08:18.200
Engrossed in painting, time flies.
[*"Dan Qing" means "Painting" in Chinese]

00:08:19.593 --> 00:08:22.512
Wealth and fame
are fleeting clouds to me.

00:08:24.793 --> 00:08:25.593
Good name.

00:08:59.433 --> 00:09:00.553
You raced all night.

00:09:00.553 --> 00:09:02.272
Why are you still so worked up?

00:09:03.073 --> 00:09:04.032
Feeling down?

00:09:06.313 --> 00:09:07.713
What's with the suspect?

00:09:07.713 --> 00:09:09.313
I just don't get him.

00:09:09.313 --> 00:09:10.632
He's seriously disturbed.

00:09:17.792 --> 00:09:18.752
Do you really like her?

00:09:20.713 --> 00:09:21.512
I do.

00:09:22.152 --> 00:09:23.473
Han Zhao is a good girl.

00:09:24.073 --> 00:09:26.433
If you really like her,
pursue her properly.

00:09:27.953 --> 00:09:29.392
So, won't you help me?

00:09:29.833 --> 00:09:30.953
If you don't help me,

00:09:31.553 --> 00:09:32.672
what if I fail?

00:09:44.392 --> 00:09:47.152
Little Zhao told me you have

00:09:47.272 --> 00:09:48.833
a longtime unrequited love.

00:09:49.272 --> 00:09:49.953
Tell me about it.

00:09:52.792 --> 00:09:53.632
Not your business.

00:10:39.912 --> 00:10:41.152
When did you start smoking?

00:10:42.233 --> 00:10:43.032
Give me one.

00:10:45.272 --> 00:10:46.272
What are you here for?

00:10:50.233 --> 00:10:51.032
What?

00:10:52.872 --> 00:10:56.752
Your little dog bite
is more telling than the suspect's.

00:10:57.992 --> 00:10:59.632
See? Teeth bite marks.

00:10:59.632 --> 00:11:00.992
We've got a lead on our case.

00:11:05.193 --> 00:11:06.872
Get back before your master sees you.

00:11:08.032 --> 00:11:08.632
Lei,

00:11:09.193 --> 00:11:10.473
I need the cigarette butt photos

00:11:10.473 --> 00:11:11.473
to compare bite marks.

00:11:26.992 --> 00:11:30.353
The bite marks on all cigarette butts
left at the crime scenes are very deep.

00:11:30.593 --> 00:11:32.872
This reflects
the suspect's smoking habit.

00:11:33.313 --> 00:11:36.152
He likely doesn't hold the cigarette
with his hand much while smoking.

00:11:36.152 --> 00:11:38.473
Instead, he bites the cigarette
to take breaths.

00:11:38.672 --> 00:11:39.473
I speculate

00:11:39.473 --> 00:11:42.113
this habit is directly related
to the nature of his work.

00:11:43.152 --> 00:11:45.752
Do you think it's possible
that some people have a habit

00:11:45.752 --> 00:11:47.672
of biting down hard on the cigarette,

00:11:48.193 --> 00:11:49.272
taking a couple of puffs,

00:11:50.392 --> 00:11:51.672
and taking it with their hand?

00:11:53.433 --> 00:11:54.512
That's possible.

00:11:54.632 --> 00:11:57.593
But that would be a specific trait,

00:11:58.313 --> 00:11:59.113
rarely occurring.

00:11:59.113 --> 00:12:00.272
And if that were the case,

00:12:00.593 --> 00:12:03.313
the bite marks should be
from the upper and lower incisors,

00:12:04.473 --> 00:12:05.752
which are narrower.

00:12:06.553 --> 00:12:09.032
But look at those photos.
They're all molar marks.

00:12:11.632 --> 00:12:12.553
It's simple.

00:12:12.553 --> 00:12:13.336
He...

00:12:14.040 --> 00:12:14.912
Just...

00:12:14.912 --> 00:12:15.713
Open wide.

00:12:17.073 --> 00:12:17.872
See?

00:12:18.073 --> 00:12:20.672
By biting the cigarette with his molars,

00:12:21.992 --> 00:12:23.473
it doesn't interfere with work

00:12:23.553 --> 00:12:25.193
or let the smoke sting his eyes.

00:12:27.096 --> 00:12:28.888
The locations of these three cases

00:12:28.888 --> 00:12:30.360
(Chen Xiaomeng, Weigang Street, Attempted Rape)
are Weigang Street,

00:12:30.360 --> 00:12:32.568
(Li Ying, Tianpeng Street, Rape)
Tianpeng Street, and Huaibei Road.

00:12:32.568 --> 00:12:33.353
(Guo Bingbing, Huaibei Road,
Rape and Murder)

00:12:33.353 --> 00:12:35.632
They're across the city's east,
west, and north areas,

00:12:36.032 --> 00:12:37.792
tens of kilometers apart.

00:12:38.392 --> 00:12:39.912
The suspect is a mobile criminal.

00:12:40.073 --> 00:12:41.872
The interval between crimes
is about 15 days.

00:12:42.713 --> 00:12:46.512
Biting cigarette butts with molars
is common among heavy manual laborers.

00:12:47.233 --> 00:12:50.953
A renovation worker
fits the suspect's profile perfectly.

00:12:51.272 --> 00:12:52.313
And coincidentally,

00:12:52.512 --> 00:12:55.833
all three scenes are surrounded
by renovation sites.

00:12:56.752 --> 00:12:59.593
Combined with the suspect's
shabby clothing

00:12:59.832 --> 00:13:01.632
(Yunxi City Map)
and poor economic status,

00:13:02.233 --> 00:13:03.433
we can first hypothesize

00:13:03.872 --> 00:13:05.912
that the suspect works at a nearby site.

00:13:06.152 --> 00:13:09.113
His stint ends in around two weeks.

00:13:09.752 --> 00:13:11.672
He chose these three locations

00:13:12.193 --> 00:13:14.392
because he happened
to be working nearby.

00:13:14.953 --> 00:13:18.392
The expensive cigarettes
were likely given by his employer.

00:13:18.392 --> 00:13:21.752
And the cheap ones
must be his own purchase.

00:13:21.752 --> 00:13:23.632
Following this reasoning,

00:13:24.953 --> 00:13:27.313
there are quite a few trades
involved in renovation.

00:13:27.953 --> 00:13:30.433
Carpenters, masons, painters,
electricians, and plumbers.

00:13:31.992 --> 00:13:34.792
That's a lot of people to investigate.

00:13:36.912 --> 00:13:39.833
We conducted
field investigations on this.

00:13:40.152 --> 00:13:42.992
Plumbers and electricians
kick up a lot of dust while working.

00:13:43.233 --> 00:13:44.752
They generally don't smoke on the job.

00:13:45.433 --> 00:13:47.353
Nor do they smoke
by biting the cigarette butt.

00:13:51.872 --> 00:13:52.553
Ruled out.

00:13:58.672 --> 00:14:00.392
Painters wear masks when spraying paint

00:14:00.752 --> 00:14:02.272
to prevent inhaling harmful fumes.

00:14:02.833 --> 00:14:03.512
Ruled out.

00:14:09.473 --> 00:14:11.593
Carpenters make up
a large portion of renovation work.

00:14:11.632 --> 00:14:12.833
They work longer terms.

00:14:12.833 --> 00:14:14.113
And wood dust is fine,

00:14:14.113 --> 00:14:15.632
hard to clean off completely.

00:14:16.713 --> 00:14:19.272
But no wood shavings
were found on any of the three victims.

00:14:19.872 --> 00:14:20.833
Ruled out too.

00:14:35.593 --> 00:14:36.313
Masons

00:14:36.953 --> 00:14:38.473
require both hands for their work

00:14:38.992 --> 00:14:40.193
and likely work short-term.

00:14:40.992 --> 00:14:42.872
And they're exposed to a lot of dust.

00:14:43.593 --> 00:14:46.512
This matches the victims' description
of the suspect's characteristics.

00:14:47.473 --> 00:14:48.872
Ye Qian, here's what you do.

00:14:48.872 --> 00:14:49.912
Notify everyone

00:14:50.073 --> 00:14:52.672
to focus on all residences
around the crime scenes,

00:14:53.272 --> 00:14:55.512
both completed renovations
and those currently underway,

00:14:55.833 --> 00:14:57.272
to check the renovation crews.

00:14:58.152 --> 00:14:59.872
Prioritize investigating them

00:15:00.073 --> 00:15:01.392
to find any leads.

00:15:01.392 --> 00:15:02.152
Got it.

00:15:04.312 --> 00:15:07.064
(Welcome
to Yehai Building Materials Mall)

00:15:17.861 --> 00:15:22.360
(Buffet Restaurant)

00:15:22.360 --> 00:15:24.408
(Meidu Concept
Decoration Engineering Co., Ltd.)

00:15:56.392 --> 00:15:57.073
Chief Xu,

00:15:57.313 --> 00:16:00.152
there are two renovation companies
that fit the criteria.

00:16:00.553 --> 00:16:02.433
Both are leading companies in the city.

00:16:02.752 --> 00:16:04.553
Each has over a hundred employees.

00:16:04.752 --> 00:16:06.872
If we DNA test everyone,

00:16:06.872 --> 00:16:08.713
