00:16:08.953 --> 00:16:11.953
I suggest we investigate covertly

00:16:12.272 --> 00:16:13.872
to avoid tipping him off.

00:16:15.353 --> 00:16:17.713
As for suspects linked to the fishpond,

00:16:17.713 --> 00:16:19.392
there are about sixty.

00:16:20.833 --> 00:16:23.392
Any with prior records among them?

00:16:23.392 --> 00:16:24.032
Yes.

00:16:24.152 --> 00:16:25.992
Three have theft records.

00:16:26.193 --> 00:16:27.713
Two with sexual assault records.

00:16:28.433 --> 00:16:29.392
And they both

00:16:30.512 --> 00:16:31.512
are masons.

00:16:31.992 --> 00:16:33.313
One is Jiang Lianhong.

00:16:33.313 --> 00:16:34.353
The other is Wang En'tai.

00:16:34.632 --> 00:16:35.353
Wang En'tai

00:16:35.353 --> 00:16:37.473
had a work injury a month ago.

00:16:37.672 --> 00:16:39.032
His leg is in a cast.

00:16:39.152 --> 00:16:40.032
He can be ruled out.

00:16:40.473 --> 00:16:41.872
Have you located Jiang Lianhong?

00:16:41.992 --> 00:16:42.953
We've sent people on it.

00:18:46.872 --> 00:18:48.313
Ouch. It's me.

00:18:48.313 --> 00:18:49.113
Qian.

00:18:49.593 --> 00:18:50.472
Why are you here?

00:18:51.952 --> 00:18:53.672
You don't know your own strength.

00:18:53.672 --> 00:18:55.113
I shouldn't have come to you.

00:19:02.793 --> 00:19:03.593
Got news?

00:19:03.872 --> 00:19:04.593
No news.

00:19:12.872 --> 00:19:14.113
I've been trying to find her

00:19:15.392 --> 00:19:16.472
for almost ten years.

00:19:18.632 --> 00:19:20.113
Maybe I was mistaken.

00:19:22.113 --> 00:19:23.712
Won't know unless we try, right?

00:19:29.232 --> 00:19:30.232
I have a friend

00:19:30.513 --> 00:19:32.313
who works at this taxi company.

00:19:39.872 --> 00:19:41.432
I've done you another big favor.

00:19:42.033 --> 00:19:43.192
Next time you cook,

00:19:43.192 --> 00:19:44.232
count me in?

00:19:46.033 --> 00:19:46.753
Get lost.

00:19:50.152 --> 00:19:51.113
A hobble for livestock.

00:19:51.672 --> 00:19:52.232
I felt

00:19:52.232 --> 00:19:54.113
I'd seen it somewhere before.

00:19:54.113 --> 00:19:55.793
It took me a while to remember.

00:19:55.912 --> 00:19:59.593
As a kid, I found something similar
in my hometown pigpen.

00:20:01.313 --> 00:20:01.952
Chief Xu.

00:20:02.232 --> 00:20:02.793
Chief Xu.

00:20:03.712 --> 00:20:04.513
Proceed.

00:20:05.353 --> 00:20:07.432
Most people
have never even seen this thing.

00:20:07.553 --> 00:20:08.872
Let alone bought it.

