Only manufacturers, vets,

00:20:12.513 --> 00:20:14.113
or vet assistants would have access.

00:20:14.313 --> 00:20:15.192
Little Qian and I

00:20:15.192 --> 00:20:18.273
searched the whole city
to buy this thing.

