One is in the Taohua Village
in the west,

00:20:39.513 --> 00:20:42.432
and the other
is in Niulangang in the south.

00:20:43.553 --> 00:20:45.553
Both farms have

00:20:45.553 --> 00:20:46.872
more than 60 people.

00:20:46.872 --> 00:20:47.912
We need to screen them all

00:20:48.033 --> 00:20:50.073
to find the key lead.

00:20:53.712 --> 00:20:55.033
Sure about these measurements?

00:20:55.033 --> 00:20:57.353
No problem. Sofas are usually 900,

00:20:57.353 --> 00:20:58.472
and coffee tables 600.

00:20:58.472 --> 00:20:59.712
They'll fit here fine.

00:21:01.073 --> 00:21:01.872
Police.

00:21:02.712 --> 00:21:04.113
Take the client to see other rooms.

00:21:04.273 --> 00:21:05.232
Okay, come with me.

00:21:06.328 --> 00:21:07.392
Where's Jiang Lianhong?

00:21:08.392 --> 00:21:11.593
H-He left.

00:21:12.553 --> 00:21:13.192
He left?

00:21:13.353 --> 00:21:14.152
Yes.

00:21:14.472 --> 00:21:17.392
Today was the last day
for the masonry work.

00:21:17.833 --> 00:21:19.912
So he left after finishing.

00:21:20.672 --> 00:21:21.593
I'm the manager.

00:21:21.593 --> 00:21:23.793
You can talk to me.

00:21:23.793 --> 00:21:24.472
