00:21:24.472 --> 00:21:25.432
Can you reach him?

00:21:26.192 --> 00:21:27.553
H-He probably went home.

00:21:28.872 --> 00:21:30.392
Reach him now. Call him.

00:21:30.833 --> 00:21:31.912
Alright.

00:21:35.273 --> 00:21:36.513
Where did I put my bag?

00:21:36.912 --> 00:21:38.513
I-I need to grab my phone.

00:22:02.793 --> 00:22:03.472
Hello?

